THE STORY OF SEXIE SADIE
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    Fifty years ago last month, on the 16th February 1968, four young
    men from Liverpool went to Rishikesh in India to study
    transcendental meditation under the spiritual guidance of the
    Maharishi Mahesh Yogi. They wanted to devote themselves to his
    instruction but unfortunately John, Paul, George and Ringo did not
    find the certainty that they were hoping for.

