NEW SATURDAY MARKET IN OLD ISLEWORTH
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Members of the local community are joining together to launch the
    Old Isleworth Market on Saturday 28 April from 10am to 2pm.
    Focusing on high quality food, the market will offer locals an
    alternative to the supermarket and a chance to purchase locally
    sourced, affordable produce.

