SOUTH WESTERN RAILWAY ENGINEERING WORKS - 8 APRIL 2018
----------------------------------------------------------------------
    
    Engineering work will affect trains from London Waterloo to Clapham
    Junction and in the Barnes area all day Sunday. Trains normally
    coming from Waterloo via Richmond will start in Richmond and go
    around the Wimbledon way. Trains going to Waterloo via Richmond
    will go to Twickenham and then go around the Wimbledon way.

